Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Project SEKAI After Talk: Reaching Out to an Unraveling Tomorrow! Hello, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Sato Hinata, the voice of Akiyama Mizuki from 25-ji, Nightcord de.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.46,0:09:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This After Talk is a stream where we look back on the event while reading the messages you've sent us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, we're focusing on the 'Reaching Out to an Unraveling Tomorrow' event.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you all enjoyed the story!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.22,0:10:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The event just ended yesterday. How was it for everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.76,0:10:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I really hope you all enjoyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.80,0:10:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a story where Mizuki really faced the future and thought about what they want to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.28,0:10:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and I think it was a very meaningful chapter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.06,0:10:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,For those of you who are at a stage where you have to decide on your education or career path, I think this story might have really resonated with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting in April, After Talk has been slightly renewed, and we've been collecting messages in advance via the official Discord and email.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much to everyone who sent one in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be reading some of your messages during the show, so please look forward to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, if you want to share your thoughts on the event or this stream, please post using the hashtag #ProsekaAfterTalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.62,0:11:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm keeping an eye on the YouTube chat, and I'll check the hashtag later too,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.50,0:11:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'll try to pick up as many interesting comments as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at the chat, there are so many international comments! I'm looking for Japanese ones... Oh, 'The ribbon is cute' and 'Your hair matches Mizuki's!'
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.08,0:11:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The stream might be a bit delayed, but people are noticing my hair and outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.42,0:11:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I always try to do this, but today I really dressed up with the card illustration in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, hello! Thank you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.64,0:11:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone said, "The story and the new song were so good I cried my eyes out."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.28,0:11:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk about the song in a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw it at home, I was like, "What is this?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, "What even is this?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I really felt the incredible effort the company put into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.80,0:11:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk more about that later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:12:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's dive right into the story of 'Reaching Out to an Unraveling Tomorrow.'
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.58,0:12:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We've received messages about the story from all of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'd like to look back on it while reading them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,First, we have a message from Kotori no Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.32,0:12:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hello, Hinata-san!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.34,0:12:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,"My child and I both enjoy playing Project SEKAI."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.14,0:12:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Mizuki-chan banner was incredibly cute, funny, and moving."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"It was wonderful to see Mizuki-chan's various feelings through their past experiences and interactions with those around them."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"I think it's very difficult to stay true to yourself and not give up on what you love when you face obstacles."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.54,0:12:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"But I believe that if you hold onto those feelings, there will come a time when they are rewarded."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.48,0:12:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"Just like the members of Nightcord, I believe there are definitely people out there
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.48,0:12:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,who will see and accept you for who you truly are."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"I really love the stories in Project SEKAI."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hinata-san, thank you so much for always voicing Mizuki."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.82,0:12:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"I will continue to support both Mizuki-chan and Hinata-san with all my heart!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.28,0:13:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, Kotori no Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.12,0:13:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In this story, Mizuki's older sister comes back from overseas,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and it starts with her opening a pop-up shop. I felt it was a huge step forward for Mizuki to want the other Nightcord members to meet her sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanade and Mafuyu had met Yuuki-san before,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.10,0:13:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but Ena met her for the first time in this story, so the relationships are really progressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Above all, Mizuki loves making videos, but they also love
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,remaking clothes, visiting boutiques, and looking at makeup. They have so many things they love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.98,0:13:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I think it's amazing that they're already facing the question of what they want to do for a career at this stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:14:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was looking at colleges, I just thought about studying something that would give me a specific skill for a job since I was paying for it, so I just went to tons of open houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My approach to finding what I liked was completely different from Mizuki's.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think this was a very important time for Mizuki to re-examine what they love at their own pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't just about the pop-up shop their sister opened;
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,realizing that their love for clothes isn't just a hobby, but something they might want to do professionally, is a huge deal. I'm just glad they could smile about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.04,0:14:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I've picked out a few scenes that I personally want to talk about, so let's take a look together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.48,0:14:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.97,0:24:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.80,0:24:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.80,0:24:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.58,0:24:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.04,0:24:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.48,0:25:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I've already made my own career choices, seeing someone else reach that moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.28,0:25:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,even if it's through witnessing it in an event story...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.12,0:25:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,well, there are always moments where you wonder if you're doing the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.64,0:25:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you can look back 10 or 20 years from now and feel glad you made that choice,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.10,0:25:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,then it was a good thing. And I think effort is what makes that possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.98,0:25:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think there's a "wrong" choice if you put in the effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.78,0:25:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you choose something and work hard at it, then in a year or two,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.28,0:25:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you might have moments where you regret it or think you shouldn't have done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.72,0:25:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But looking back after 10 or 20 years, I'm sure you'll see how it all connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.48,0:25:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll think, "If I hadn't done that then, I wouldn't be able to do this now."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.28,0:25:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you're in a different profession, I think you'll feel that way. For those of you who are working hard now,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.00,0:26:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,or have something you want to work hard at, I hope this event story gives you the courage to make that decision and keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.52,0:26:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,With that said, I'd like to talk about the illustrations next.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.74,0:26:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me read another message.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.72,0:26:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is from Meshi-meshi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.44,0:26:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Comment: 0,0:26:23.42,0:26:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.42,0:26:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.54,0:26:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I always enjoy playing Proseka.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.96,0:26:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The 4-star cards this time, especially the Mizuki illustration, were so good that I pulled the gacha desperately...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.88,0:26:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and I managed to get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.88,0:26:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This illustration, much like 'Secret Distance' or 'Where Shall This Path Lead,'
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.44,0:26:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,features a space filled with torsos, similar to Mizuki's post-training art.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.30,0:26:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Torsos appear quite often in Mizuki's illustrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.28,0:26:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They aren't exactly mannequins, but dress forms for clothes, like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.04,0:26:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.70,0:26:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.36,0:26:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.08,0:26:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,These are called torsos.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.20,0:27:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Like in 'Reaching Out for an Unattainable Tomorrow,' there's a torso.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.84,0:27:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an illustration where Mizuki is in a space with torsos.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.68,0:27:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually, the torso space has been used to represent Mizuki's dark feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.78,0:27:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but this time, they've felt the warmth of family and friends and are looking forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.06,0:27:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The space has become one that expresses Mizuki's bright and cheerful feelings, and I'm so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.88,0:27:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to see this change in Mizuki's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.42,0:27:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing but respect for the staff who create such wonderful scenarios,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.20,0:27:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and the voice actors who give the characters such depth and amazing expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.26,0:27:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for always creating such wonderful events.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.46,0:27:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take care of yourselves and keep up the good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.12,0:27:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep supporting you as a fan of Nightcord.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.78,0:27:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.96,0:27:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The colors in the illustration are quite rare for Nightcord.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.68,0:27:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We've had pale colors before, but seeing Nightcord bathed in sunlight...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.84,0:27:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's partly because they don't go outside much,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.02,0:28:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,so seeing Nightcord during the day is rare. I felt this specific touch was quite unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.32,0:28:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just Mizuki, but everyone's cards were great. The artists did an amazing job on both the pre- and post-training art.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.34,0:28:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm truly grateful. We've received comments from the illustration team regarding the outfits this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.46,0:28:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'd like to introduce those as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.28,0:28:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The comments mention that this kind of 'pure brightness' is rare for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.96,0:28:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuki, having been accepted by Nightcord, wants to create clothes that can help children...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.08,0:28:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,who are struggling with the same worries or who can't bring themselves to like who they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.88,0:28:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspired by the story of Mizuki thinking about a future career in fashion,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.30,0:28:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the design expresses the image of a future that they've finally started to envision.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.50,0:28:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They intentionally chose a simple and clean dress design with fewer elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.48,0:28:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,As a focal point, they used the yellow daisy embroidery...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.70,0:29:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,from Mizuki's new unit outfit to convey the message of 'being yourself.'
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.02,0:29:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This resulted in a simple outfit design unique to Mizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.56,0:29:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,To reflect the song's calm, warm impression and the faint hope for the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.40,0:29:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that Mizuki has begun to hold, the colors were kept soft and gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.08,0:29:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the comment we received.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.28,0:29:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, the colors across all the characters' cards are quite pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.28,0:29:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And did everyone notice that the daisies were included?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.00,0:29:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The daisies are there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.42,0:29:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see comments about the daisies now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.95,0:29:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.07,0:29:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.66,0:29:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The blue traffic light was also very striking.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.12,0:29:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.92,0:29:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuki was born in summer, in August... Happy Birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.58,0:29:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to say it so casually, but Happy Birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.20,0:29:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's summer, but I feel like Mizuki hasn't had many summer-themed illustrations until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.64,0:29:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I always felt they often wore long sleeves or clothes that covered their skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.64,0:29:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Though there were things like T-shirts before.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.64,0:30:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So, seeing an illustration that feels like summer the moment you look at it is really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.74,0:30:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,With that said, let's talk while actually looking at the card illustrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.20,0:30:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on the monitor right now, on everyone's screens.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.64,0:30:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,At least, I believe I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.08,0:30:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,First, Mizuki's pre-training card.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.24,0:30:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This illustration...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.92,0:30:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The way the older sister is smiling so happily at Mizuki reminds me of the New Year's event,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.28,0:30:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,where Yuki-san gave a ribbon to Mizuki when they were young.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.44,0:30:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And Mizuki's expression while showing off the outfit is just incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.56,0:30:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this is a pre-training card.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.24,0:30:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.44,0:30:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I love this atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.84,0:30:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And what you see in the background there is the torso.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.92,0:30:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's look at the post-training card.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.79,0:31:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.48,0:31:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.12,0:31:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Butterflies and ribbons have always been very symbolic for Mizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.24,0:31:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In those moments, I usually had an image of Mizuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.84,0:31:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,holding scissors in the illustrations. But this time, there are no scissors, just a very bright space.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.30,0:31:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though their mouth is covered, you just know they're smiling. That expression is so precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.84,0:31:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.44,0:31:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My child is such a good kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.48,0:31:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up is Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.64,0:31:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great to see Yuki-san here as well.
Comment: 0,0:31:39.52,0:31:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.52,0:31:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I love how Ena is meeting Big Sister for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.58,0:31:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and she's just totally overwhelmed by her pushy personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.76,0:31:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.00,0:31:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you haven't seen the event story yet, please check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.20,0:31:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing all of Nightcord at 25:00 talking with Big Sister is a must-see.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.96,0:32:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up, isn't this Ena amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.48,0:32:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I think girls with their hair tucked behind their ears are great, and this illustration...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.68,0:32:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,is just incredibly good.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.20,0:32:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I honestly thought she was a florist.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.72,0:32:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ena looks so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.04,0:32:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.48,0:32:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The way she's looking down slightly is also wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.22,0:32:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ena is just so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.40,0:32:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is Len.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.26,0:32:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so cute how he's eating the souvenir from Big Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.82,0:32:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.88,0:32:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is this so adorable?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.32,0:32:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that were a protein bar, it would still be cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.96,0:32:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just always eating something.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.29,0:32:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.80,0:32:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving on to the Trained version.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.08,0:32:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this insane?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.36,0:32:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.76,0:32:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking, only you could pull off short shorts like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.88,0:32:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.19,0:32:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.20,0:32:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just so grateful for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.60,0:32:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The overall style is quite rare for Nightcord, which is really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.56,0:33:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he holding a book about daisy flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.60,0:33:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My knowledge of daisies is a bit shallow, but I'm pretty sure that's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.84,0:33:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.72,0:33:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea of sharing something delicious is so sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.48,0:33:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything tastes better when you share it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.36,0:33:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.28,0:33:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanade.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.60,0:33:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.68,0:33:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,These clothes look exactly like something Mizuki or Yuki-san would pick out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.96,0:33:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.32,0:33:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks a little troubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.72,0:33:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course, it suits her perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.10,0:33:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Setting aside where she'd actually wear it, I wonder if Kanade would really wear that headpiece when she goes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.76,0:33:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not really sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.40,0:33:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.72,0:33:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I think if it looks good on her, she should definitely wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.68,0:33:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She's truly adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.96,0:33:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is always so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.72,0:33:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now for the Trained version.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.96,0:33:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks like a young lady from a wealthy family.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.16,0:33:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if these are daisies too?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.88,0:33:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones on her chest and her head.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.24,0:34:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.32,0:34:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In the side story, Kanade being forced to try on all those different clothes is also super cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.64,0:34:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you'll all take a look at the side story as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.92,0:34:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is just saying how cute they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.72,0:34:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.28,0:34:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.48,0:34:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like it's quite rare to see Nightcord wearing white.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.68,0:34:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've realized that after doing all these After Talks.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.72,0:34:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mafuyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.88,0:34:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.64,0:34:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.96,0:34:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It might not be a full smile, but seeing Mafuyu with more of a grin made me so happy and brightened my heart during this event story.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.04,0:34:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's wonderful that all the illustrations have such a sense of warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.88,0:34:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.76,0:34:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.80,0:34:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that was the illustration corner. Moving on...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.68,0:35:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Parsley Onuma wrote a new song specifically for this event.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.12,0:35:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to watch the 3DMV for "Kazarite" and talk about the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.44,0:35:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we watch the 3DMV, I'd like to share some comments we received from the Sega 3DMV production team.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.08,0:35:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In the 3DMV for "Kazarite," we used the visual of falling into water to express Mizuki's wavering emotions that they can't honestly share with the other members.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.02,0:35:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, we used the insert function and spent a lot of time on the underwater falling sequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.12,0:35:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We went through a lot of trial and error to achieve this expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.52,0:35:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There are still challenges in fully depicting a character's state of mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.22,0:35:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but we hope you'll enjoy this new form of expression through Mizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.68,0:35:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.70,0:35:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's take a look at the 3DMV.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.62,0:35:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.00,0:37:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see that face just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.92,0:38:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She was smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.80,0:38:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That was so good.
Comment: 0,0:38:03.24,0:38:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.24,0:38:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.00,0:38:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really blown away when I saw this 3DMV.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.24,0:38:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't believe how much the scenery changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.20,0:38:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes from a school setting to an after-school vibe, with leaves visible through the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.44,0:38:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and then light hitting the hallway as you walk... Oh, it's not Wi-Fi.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.08,0:38:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.40,0:38:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not exactly dust, but you can see little motes in the air. The direction is so detailed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.92,0:38:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering how they did that. It was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.48,0:38:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The way the camera pans and the characters switch was so impressive, it really surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.20,0:38:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.84,0:38:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the kind of video you want to watch over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.44,0:38:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The 2DMV is also incredible, so please check that out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.72,0:38:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,As for the 2DMV, this is just something I personally felt,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.08,0:39:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,since it hasn't been explicitly stated and I haven't heard the full details yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.08,0:39:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,In the 2DMV, there's a scene that looks like a birthday party, with a seat of honor,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.24,0:39:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and Mizuki is there with a cake. The camera pans across symbolic items,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.08,0:39:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,showing things like the letter from their older sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.90,0:39:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and ribbons. The 2D version was really great too.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.96,0:39:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of them were amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.00,0:39:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised by how much information was packed into them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.96,0:39:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, regarding the song, I felt that Mizuki's lyrics often had a lot of painful words until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.60,0:39:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not comparing it to past songs, but I felt this one has many more positive lyrics.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.40,0:39:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, there are still fluctuating emotions within Mizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.92,0:40:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think Mizuki is the type to show all their emotions. So, I consulted with the director about the nuances,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.52,0:40:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,discussing how much 'strength' to add or subtract while we created the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.54,0:40:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There are parts where the sound becomes like a radio,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.00,0:40:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and I asked if I could make my voice a bit raspy to show more emotion. We discussed many nuances like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.32,0:40:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you enjoy both the full 2DMV and the 3DMV where Mizuki smiles at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.12,0:40:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Both are already uploaded to the official Project Sekai YouTube channel,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.88,0:40:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so please check them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.56,0:40:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And with that, our short time together is up. This concludes the Project Sekai After Talk for 'Reaching Out to an Unraveling Tomorrow'.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.58,0:40:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To everyone watching the stream, what did you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.20,0:40:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a look at the comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.75,0:40:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.34,0:41:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone said Onuma Parsley's MV and the Nightcord 2D version have different vibes, and both are good.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.38,0:41:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.24,0:41:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,For Mizuki, how should I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.08,0:41:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As a student thinking about their future... Project Sekai is also approaching its 5th anniversary.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.00,0:41:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuki has been through a lot leading up to the 5th anniversary. In the midst of that, they're looking forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.24,0:41:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like saying, 'This happened, but I'm going to do my best anyway.'
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.36,0:41:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the Nightcord version of 'Kazarite' expresses that feeling of 'I'm going to try my best.'
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.36,0:41:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But Onuma-san's version...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.80,0:41:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.58,0:41:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a working adult who's tired but still trying their best to look forward and encourage themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.94,0:41:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized that even with the same lyrics, the song's range can be so wide depending on the singer and the expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.16,0:41:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I really felt that with 'Kazarite'. Please check out Onuma-san's...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.68,0:41:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it called a 2D version? What would you call it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.92,0:41:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.50,0:41:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The music video?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.90,0:42:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you enjoy that MV as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.68,0:42:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking back, many Nightcord stories have been quite heavy, exposing parts that make it hard to breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.54,0:42:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think this event story is something that high schoolers,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.68,0:42:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,can really relate to on a personal level.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.72,0:42:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Things like deciding on a career path,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.36,0:42:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,or lacking the confidence to accept and love the things you enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.40,0:42:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If there are people feeling that way right now, it's not just students, but adults too.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.72,0:42:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,For those who haven't seen the story or heard the song yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.32,0:43:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,there might be words that resonate with you precisely because of who you are right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.12,0:43:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope everyone, both adults and students, enjoys it to the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.48,0:43:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you haven't finished the story for 'Reaching Out to an Unraveling Tomorrow', you can read it all from the event archives once the next event starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.82,0:43:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give it a read.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.86,0:43:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It will also likely be uploaded to YouTube at a later date,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.14,0:43:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's perfectly fine to wait for that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.56,0:43:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We are always looking for messages for the After Talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.62,0:43:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You can send them through the After Talk channel on the official Project Sekai Discord or via email.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.72,0:43:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please send them in when the next After Talk event is held.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.86,0:43:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We look forward to your messages regarding the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.70,0:43:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,August is almost over, and September is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.80,0:43:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And once September is over, the Anniversary Festival will be waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.00,0:44:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been steadily preparing for it, so please look forward to that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.64,0:44:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,August might be ending, but the heat certainly isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.88,0:44:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be careful of heatstroke. If you feel like it's too much,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.00,0:44:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,it's perfectly fine to run away from the heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.56,0:44:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Keeping cool is the most important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.48,0:44:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope to see you all at the Anniversary Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.76,0:44:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be waiting for you at the venue too.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.96,0:44:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you all for watching until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.50,0:44:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all survive the summer together. I'll see you all again soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.44,0:44:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.52,0:44:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
